      "pattern": "I parry / I block (an attack)",
      "hint": "In Exalted, parry uses Parry DV (Static value; no roll needed unless adding charms). Note the character's stored Parry DV and any active charm modifiers."
    },
    {
      "pattern": "I dodge / I evade (an attack)",
      "hint": "In Exalted, dodge uses Evasion DV (Static value; no roll). Note Evasion DV; subtract -1 onslaught penalty for each successive attack this round."
    },
    {
      "pattern": "I attack with my weapon",
      "hint": "In Exalted, an attack rolls Attribute + Ability + accuracy bonus + Charm dice. Mention the relevant pool and check whether the player is invoking any Charms before resolving."
    },
    {
      "pattern": "I spend essence / motes",
      "hint": "Track the spend separately for Personal and Peripheral pools. Personal-only Charms must come from Personal motes; mixed Charms allow the player to choose. Update anima banner if Peripheral spend exceeds threshold."
    },
    {
      "pattern": "I roll initiative / join battle",
      "hint": "Exalted uses Join Battle (Wits + Awareness) at combat start; initiative is then a fluid tracker that rises/falls with combat actions. Don't roll a fresh JB if combat is already underway."
